36
00:08:26,030 --> 00:08:26,930
Our Economics teacher?

37
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:29,290
Yes, sir. Our Economics teacher

38
00:08:30,030 --> 00:08:30,930
No man!

39
00:08:32,230 --> 00:08:35,430
Ya man. I know Miss. Kashyap
better than you

40
00:08:38,670 --> 00:08:39,160
Tuitions...

41
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,870
