186
00:25:20,410 --> 00:25:24,180
Just decide, Sameer. You can
either be with Akash or me!

187
00:25:30,990 --> 00:25:31,550
I am thinking...

188
00:25:32,390 --> 00:25:35,050
You need time to think
if you want to be with me!

189
00:25:38,700 --> 00:25:40,460
Okay. So you want some time?

190
00:25:40,770 --> 00:25:41,230
No!

191
00:25:44,370 --> 00:25:47,100
I'm going out with friends.
I'll be back by 2.00

192
00:25:47,940 --> 00:25:52,340
If I don't hear from you before that,
I'll know what your answer is

193
00:25:57,120 --> 00:25:59,280
Don't you think you are
over-reacting?

194
00:26:01,790 --> 00:26:02,280
No

195
00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:08,880
You've never seen me over-react.
If I do... then God help you!!

196
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:32,040
What are you doing!

197
00:26:32,950 --> 00:26:37,480
Your bruise has turned a strange colour.
Have you seen it, Sid?

198
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:39,750
I'm glad you like it!
Do you want one?

199
00:26:40,290 --> 00:26:43,890
Hey! Don't get that anger out on me man

200
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,990
Did I ask you to speak to Shalini?

201
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:51,260
No. But you could've at least helped me.
You just sat there!

202
00:26:51,800 --> 00:26:55,370
Such a true friend! I think I'd be
better off befriending Rohit

203
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:56,740
I'd at least get some protection!

204
00:26:59,550 --> 00:27:01,740
May God bless your unity. I'm off.

205
00:27:02,280 --> 00:27:04,410
Where to? -Home.

206
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:06,650
Why? What's the hurry?
Right, Sameer?

207
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:09,080
Ya, man, chill. It's only
1'O' clock

208
00:27:10,690 --> 00:27:12,850
In which country?
It's nearly 4 here!

209
00:27:31,480 --> 00:27:32,810
I forgot to call Priya!

210
00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:38,050
Why are you so scared of Priya?

211
00:27:38,420 --> 00:27:39,410
I'm not scared of her

212
00:27:40,350 --> 00:27:43,120
I don't want to hurt her
or lose her

213
00:27:43,790 --> 00:27:47,190
Sameer, I can't understand
how you tolerate her

214
00:27:47,560 --> 00:27:49,050
She seems more a boss
than a girlfriend!

215
00:27:50,330 --> 00:27:54,200
Akash, I'm asking for help,
not your expert comments

216
00:27:54,400 --> 00:27:55,030
What should I do?

217
00:27:56,340 --> 00:27:57,060
What do you think?

218
00:27:57,940 --> 00:28:00,530
I'll tell you what.
Call Priya and apologise

219
