693
01:25:40,060 --> 01:25:41,320
I still remember that night

694
01:25:49,470 --> 01:25:51,770
I never thought things would go
that far

695
01:25:58,180 --> 01:25:59,270
I couldn't sleep all night

696
01:26:00,850 --> 01:26:02,340
I went and met Akash
the next morning

697
01:26:42,290 --> 01:26:44,120
These things happen
between friends

698
01:26:44,590 --> 01:26:47,920
Let's go meet Sid.
He must be feeling bad too

699
01:26:50,200 --> 01:26:52,100
