must feel

718
01:28:59,860 --> 01:29:03,020
You know I was just kidding,
don't you?

719
01:29:06,730 --> 01:29:07,760
Don't worry about it

720
01:29:08,430 --> 01:29:09,830
You weren't the only one who was
kidding

721
