wants me to manage...

738
01:30:49,770 --> 01:30:52,670
Let's see how long it lasts now.
And you?

739
01:30:53,810 --> 01:30:54,970
My uncle lives there

740
01:30:55,410 --> 01:30:57,710
My mother's brother.
I'm visiting him

741
01:30:58,240 --> 01:30:59,140
He's nothing like Rohit, is he!

742
01:31:03,580 --> 01:31:04,240
What does he do?

743
