Have you been to Sydney before?

744
01:31:11,320 --> 01:31:12,880
Do you always ask so many
questions?

745
01:31:13,430 --> 01:31:15,720
Yes. Have you been to Sydney
before?

746
01:31:16,530 --> 01:31:17,000
Yes

747
