with him?

751
01:31:34,250 --> 01:31:35,150
I said I'm sorry

752
01:31:35,880 --> 01:31:38,110
Okay but I will have to ask
my uncle

753
01:31:40,290 --> 01:31:41,880
But he won't refuse.

754
01:31:42,520 --> 01:31:42,990
Why?

755
01:31:43,760 --> 01:31:45,020
Because I have bought him a gift!

756
01:32:17,790 --> 01:32:19,950
I'm fine but please stop
calling me uncle now

757
01:32:20,160 --> 01:32:22,490
You've grown up which makes us
practically the same age

758
01:32:33,810 --> 01:32:34,900
So, is it a business trip?

759
01:32:35,110 --> 01:32:38,870
